question: Please provide me the number of immunizations uncovered by the payer Anthem.
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  COUNT(DISTINCT i.code)
FROM immunizations AS i
JOIN encounters AS e
  ON i.encounter = e.id
JOIN payers AS p
  ON e.payer = p.id
WHERE
  p.name = 'Anthem' AND i.code NOT IN (
    SELECT
      code
    FROM medications AS m
    JOIN payers AS p2
      ON m.payer = p2.id
    WHERE
      p2.name = 'Anthem'
  );
```

question: Which procedure codes did the patient named Colette720 Hamill307 undergo?
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  p.first || ' ' || p.last AS patient_name,
  p.birthdate AS patient_birthdate,
  proc.code AS procedure_code,
  proc.start AS procedure_start_date,
  enc.start AS encounter_start_date,
  enc.end AS encounter_end_date,
  org.name AS organization_name,
  org.city AS organization_city,
  org.address AS organization_address
FROM patients AS p
LEFT JOIN procedures AS proc
  ON p.id = proc.patient
LEFT JOIN encounters AS enc
  ON proc.encounter = enc.id
LEFT JOIN organizations AS org
  ON enc.organization = org.id
WHERE
  p.first LIKE '%Colette720%' AND p.last LIKE '%Hamill307%';
```

  p.name LIKE '%Medicaid%' /* Filtering the results to include payers with 'Medicaid' in their names using LIKE operator */

[Q]: What are unique set of patients that have covered and uncovered procedures for the same encounter with the INSURANCE_TYPE 'HEALTH'
[SQL]: 
```sql
SELECT
  DISTINCT
  p.id,
  p.first,
  p.last
FROM patients AS p
LEFT JOIN encounters AS e
  ON p.id = e.patient
LEFT JOIN procedures AS pr
  ON e.id = pr.encounter
LEFT JOIN claims AS c
  ON e.id = c.encounter
LEFT JOIN payers AS payer
  ON c.payerid = payer.id
WHERE
  payer.name = 'HEALTH'
  AND EXISTS(
    SELECT
      1
    FROM procedures
    WHERE
      encounter = e.id AND payer_coverage IS NULL
  )
  AND EXISTS(
    SELECT
      1
    FROM procedures
    WHERE
      encounter = e.id AND payer_coverage IS NOT NULL
  );
```

question: What is the successrate of medication 72 HR Fentanyl 0.025 MG/HR Transdermal System?
answers:
SELECT
  MED.DESCRIPTION AS Medication_Name,
  COUNT(DISTINCT P.ID) AS Number_of_Patients_Prescribed,
  COUNT(DISTINCT P.ID) FILTER (WHERE RX.ReasonCode = '748102') AS Num_of_Patients_who_stopped
FROM Medications AS MED
JOIN Prescriptions AS RX
  ON MED.DESCRIPTION = RX.Medication
JOIN Patients AS P
  ON RX.PatientID = P.ID
WHERE
  MED.DESCRIPTION = '72 HR Fentanyl 0.025 MG/HR Transdermal System'
GROUP BY
  1
ORDER BY
  Number_of_Patients_Prescribed DESC;

question: Can you tell me when the observation Body mass index (BMI) [Ratio] was recorded?
answers: SELECT DISTINCT o.address, o.city, o.state, o.zip FROM organizations o LEFT JOIN encounters e ON o.id=e.organization LEFT JOIN patients p ON e.patient = p.id LEFT JOIN payer_transitions pt ON p.id=pt.patient WHERE pt.plan_ownership='primary'

question: Please provide me the patients who have received the immunization with code 140.
answers:
SELECT DISTINCT p.first, p.last 
FROM patients p 
LEFT JOIN immunizations i ON p.id=i.patient 
WHERE i.code='140';

question: Who is the patient associated with the claim cca769d0-09e0-72f9-23aa-e6ddb2200792?
answers:
SELECT distinct p.first, p.last 
FROM patients p 
LEFT JOIN claims c ON p.id=c.patientid 
WHERE c.id='cca769d0-09e0-72f9-23aa-e6ddb2200792';

question: Please provide me the number of immunizations uncovered by the payer Cigna Health.
answers:
```sql
SELECT
  COUNT(DISTINCT (
    i.code
  ))
FROM immunizations AS i
JOIN payers AS p
  ON i.payer = p.id
WHERE
  p.name = 'Cigna Health' AND i.BASE_COST < 0;
```

question: Who has been treated with the procedure Depression screening using Patient Health Questionnaire Nine Item score (procedure)?
answers:
SELECT DISTINCT p.first, p.last
FROM procedures pr
LEFT JOIN patients p ON pr.patient = p.id
LEFT JOIN encounters e ON pr.encounter = e.id
WHERE pr.description = 'Depression screening using Patient Health Questionnaire Nine Item score (procedure)';

question: What is the encounter associated with the immunization Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free?
answers: SELECT DISTINCT e.description FROM encounters e JOIN immunizations i ON e.id = i.encounter WHERE i.description = 'Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free';
